{
  "texts": [
    "It is evident that the model was capable of producing questions with high accuracy and comprehensiveness.",
    "Subsequently, the model's ability to generate functional analysis was assessed by a TRIZ expert based on the criteria outlined in Section title \"Functional analysis generation evaluation\", and the results were documented in Table 7.",
    "While the model was capable of generating a comprehensive functional analysis, its accuracy was around 50 percent.",
    "In the initial case study, 310 items were recognized in the extracted interactions, comprising 108 unique items and the remaining being duplicates.",
    "Of the 108 unique items, 61 were identified as tools or objects, while 47 could not be classified as such according to TRIZ concepts."
  ]
}